Notes: UWO's season opener...UWO got 18 points, 9 rebounds and 3 assists from Porath
and 15 points, 8 rebounds and 3 assists from Campbell...SMU got 18 points and
6 rebounds from Vesel...A 19-5 scoring run gave UWO a 49-31 lead with 4:45 to
play in the third quarter...UWO took 14-12 lead and led the rest of the game.
Game.Officials: Jodi Duffe,  Austin Edge,  Mark Repinski
